[I] Simple audio effects

[T] This application was formerly known as PulseEffects, but it was renamed to
[T] Easy Effects after it started to use GTK4 and GStreamer usage was replaced
[T] by native PipeWire filters. And eventually the whole application was ported
[T] from GTK4 to a combination of Qt, QML and KDE/Kirigami frameworks.

[U] https://github.com/wwmm/easyeffects

[A] wwmm
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL3
[V] 8.2.0

[D] fe96e9c0cd74ba033727dda9da4382e1ba87d99255bcae5204a7f0b3 easyeffects-8.2.0.tar.gz https://github.com/wwmm/easyeffects/archive/v8.2.0/

. $base/package/*/*/kde-conf.in
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' "-L$root$(pkgprefix libdir glib)"
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' "-L$root$(pkgprefix libdir qt6base)"
